Congratulations to the following Onteora High School music ensemble members, who performed at the annual New York State School Music Association (NYSSMA) Area All-State Festival held at Suffern High School on November 22 and 23:
Band: Marisa Mayone and Dylan Wiswall;
Mixed Chorus: Grace Foster;
Orchestra: Joey Driscoll, Sophia Grinberg, Julian Jordaan-Grady, Archie Lewis-Harris, Maxwell Mielcarek, Jason Zheng.
Selection to these groups were based upon NYSSMA Solo Festival scores from last spring. The mission of NYSSMA is to advance music education across New York State for its membership and students in member school programs.

